elements.title: Willem van Ruytenburch
elements.contents: ... that Willem van Ruytenburch (pictured) became more famous after his death, as the "man dressed in yellow" in Rembrandt's The Night Watch, than he was during his life as a Dutch social climber?

elements.title: All Ghillied Up

elements.title: Viran Rydkvist

elements.title: Letters Written in France
elements.contents: ... that Helen Maria Williams's Letters Written in France praised the French Revolution even though she was imprisoned during the Reign of Terror for being English?

elements.title: the 1911 benefit game

elements.title: Nilima Arun Kshirsagar
elements.contents: ... that Nilima Arun Kshirsagar developed and patented liposomal amphotericin B, which was used to treat "black fungus" during the COVID-19 pandemic in India?
